title: Fenerbahce 1-1 Manchester United: What Were The Main Talking Points As United’s Wait For A Maiden Europa League Victory Goes On?
description: Suffering a second-half collapse in Istanbul on Thursday night, Manchester United were forced to settle for a 1-1 stalemate away at Fenerbahce.
